# CCNA Study Repository

This repository contains structured study materials for the **Cisco CCNA 200-301** exam.

---

## 🚀 Start Here

Before using any material in this repository, read this Reddit guide:

--> **CCNA Study Guide – A Definitive Guide**  
https://www.reddit.com/r/ccna/comments/1c3nmoa/ccna_study_guide_a_definitive_guide/

This guide explains:
- Study order
- Best resources
- Lab strategy
- Exam expectations
- Recommended mindset
---

## 📚 Recommended Study Order

1. Read **Exam topics.pdf**
2. Follow the Reddit guide (linked above)
3. Study using:
   - Official Cert Guide Volume 1
   - Official Cert Guide Volume 2
4. Do labs (JIT-Labs / Extra Labs)
5. Review Cheat Sheets
6. Final review with:
   - 31 Days Before Your CCNA Exam
